      <title>欧洲央行第五次会议维持利率稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-11/ecb-holds-rates-steady-for-fifth-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行周四将存款利率维持在创纪录的4%，同时发出明确信号，即通胀降温将很快允许其开始降息。莉兹·伯登 (Lizzy Burden) 接受彭博电视台报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-11/ecb-holds-rates-steady-for-fifth-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 12:34:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行维持利率不变，发出开始降息的最明确信号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/ecb-holds-interest-rates-and-firms-path-to-first-cut-in-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行第五次会议维持利率不变，同时发出迄今为止最明确的信号，即通胀降温将很快允许其开始降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/ecb-holds-interest-rates-and-firms-path-to-first-cut-in-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 12:21:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
